OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely cloudy with drizzly showers on
OL,7,FMonday. Turning drier and brighter
OL,8,Ffrom Tuesday with temperatures around
OL,9,Fthe seasonal average.
